            <title><![CDATA[Game Pass Ultimate's Price Hike Was Quietly Paired With Another Downside]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/game-pass-ultimates-price-hike-was-quietly-paired-with-another-downside/1100-6535197/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/game-pass-ultimates-price-hike-was-quietly-paired-with-another-downside.1315708/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6535197">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Microsoft has <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/game-pass-price-hike-announced-now-costs-30-month-for-ultimate/1100-6535138/" data-ref-id="1100-6535138">raised the price of Xbox Game Pass Ultimate by 50%</a> and offered some additional perks like <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/94-new-game-pass-games-released-today-heres-the-full-list/2900-7083/" data-ref-id="2900-7083">more games</a>, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-are-fortnite-crew-and-ubisoft-classics-the-new-game-pass-ultimate-perks/1100-6535143/" data-ref-id="1100-6535143">access to Fortnite Crew</a>, and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-cloud-gaming-exits-beta-with-some-improvements/1100-6535146/" data-ref-id="1100-6535146">better cloud streaming</a>--but Microsoft is also removing a previous perk as well.</p><p><a href="https://x.com/charlieINTEL/status/1973938451830747279" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">CharlieIntel has discovered</a> that Xbox Game Pass Ultimate members no longer get 10% off Call of Duty Points or BlackCell bundles. The change appears to have gone into effect recently. This discount was a pretty nice perk for regular Call of Duty players who buy DLC.</p><p>People are roasting Microsoft for the recent Xbox Game Pass changes in all manner of ways, including <a href="https://x.com/WillieBBurner/status/1973938858908844495" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">through Mr. Krabs memes about being greedy.</a></p><p>Microsoft is <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsoft-is-raising-xbox-prices-in-the-us-again/1100-6534892/" data-ref-id="1100-6534892">raising Game Pass and console prices</a> and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-layoffs-begin-with-200-cuts-in-europe-report/1100-6532905/" data-ref-id="1100-6532905">laying thousands off</a> at a time when the company <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/investor/earnings/fy-2025-q4/press-release-webcast" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener">made $27.2 billion in <em>profit </em>in a period of about 90 days.</a> CEO Satya Nadella recently acknowledged the cuts, saying <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-microsofts-ceo-told-employees-about-ai-and-future-of-company-after-mass-layoffs/1100-6533420/" data-ref-id="1100-6533420">the "enigma of success" and pursuit of profit can be "messy."</a></p><p>Microsoft recently <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsoft-reached-4-trillion-valuation-after-mass-layoffs/1100-6533588/" data-ref-id="1100-6533588">passed $4 trillion in total market cap</a>, becoming just the second company ever, joining Nvidia, to reach those heights. Microsoft's market cap has since retreated to around $3.8 trillion.</p><p>In other Call of Duty news, the <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/call-of-duty-black-ops-7-beta-start-time-how-to-get-in-and-everything-else-to-know/1100-6534073/" data-ref-id="1100-6534073">Black Ops 7 multiplayer beta</a> is going on now, and it's available now for people who preorder, have Game Pass Ultimate, or find a code another way. The open beta begins on October 5.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
                                  </div>


          
  
    
          
            
