      </div>
        
      </section>
    
            
    </article></div><br/><br/>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/halo-combat-evolved-remake-coming-from-oblivion-remastered-dev-report/1100-6535196/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
